Date: Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:14:11 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] tools: add GitHub Linguist submission materials

Add resources/syntax_highlighting/stl/github_linguist/ with the four
snippets needed to register Sen STL in github-linguist/linguist
(languages.yml, grammars.yml, heuristics.yml entries) plus a submission
guide and sample-selection guidance.

The heuristic disambiguates between Sen STL and the existing
stereolithography STL registration by looking for a package declaration
or any STL declaration keyword near the top of the file.

Link the new subdirectory from the top-level syntax_highlighting README.

